  "description": "A plenty of new vanilla-faithful armors sets with custom effects applied.",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\"> \n\t<img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FL8wS3F.png\"> \n</p>\n\n<center> \n\t<a href=\"https://github.com/aleganza/Plenty-Of-Armors\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/v/release/aleganza/plenty-of-armors?color=1F96B1&labelColor=0F5875&label=&logo=github&logoColor=FFFFFF&style=for-the-badge\">\n\t</a>\n\t<a href=\"https://discord.gg/ZDnc7A5kBY\" target=\"_blank\">\n                <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1095353671304351774?color=1F96B1&labelColor=0F5875&label=&logo=discord&logoColor=FFFFFF&style=for-the-badge\">\n\t</a>\n\t<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/aleganza\" target=\"_blank\">\n                <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?color=1F96B1&labelColor=0F5875&label=&logo=kofi&logoColor=FFFFFF&message=donate&style=for-the-badge\">\n\t</a>\n</center>\n\n<br>\n\n<center> \n\t<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api/\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rDYdzzb.png\"> \n\t</a>\n</center>\n\n<br>\n\n<center>\nBored of the same old armors? Well you're in the right place! <b>Plenty of Armors</b> adds many unique sets and items while maintaining vanilla look and mechanics.\n</center>\n\n<br>\n\n<a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/PixelDream\">\n        <img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Plenty_of_Armors/BH_PoA_promo.webp\">\n</a>\n\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Plenty_of_Armors/BH_PoA_features.webp\">\n\n* 32 new armors;\n* 9 brand new items (also findable in loot chests);\n* Custom advancements;\n* Custom effects applied when full armor sets are equipped.\n\n<img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Plenty_of_Armors/BH_PoA_showcase.webp\">\n\n<a href=\"https://minecraftstorage.com/mods/plenty-of-armors\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HBwW53q.png\"> \n</a>\n\n<center>\n  <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/BohqcRAZGf8\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n  <img width='100%' src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iAKwasy.png\">\n</center>\n\n## 🧾 Armors List:\n\n### 👶 Early Game:\n\n<p align=\"center\"> \n\t<img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/z9cm9C4.jpg\"> \n\t<p align=\"center\"> \n</p>\n\n### 🧑 Mid Game:\n\n<p align=\"center\"> \n\t<img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zLodGZB.jpg\"> \n\t<p align=\"center\"> \n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\"> \n\t<img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/krjL8ey.jpg\"> \n\t<p align=\"center\"> \n</p>\n\n###  👴 Late Game::\n<p align=\"center\"> \n\t<img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/av3pHND.jpg\"> \n\t<p align=\"center\"> \n</p>\n\n### Craftings\n\nAll items are integrated into the vanilla recipe book (and any mod like JEI or NEI).\nOfficial Online Wiki is currently under development.\n\n### Mod Conflicts\n\nIn order to avoid crafting recipe conflicts with other mods, we recommend using <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/polymorph-fabric\">this mod</a>.\n\n### Recommended Mods\n\nWe recommend using <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/armorpoints\">this mod</a> since some Armors exceed the number of armor points in the GUI.\n\n### Bugs and Issues\n\nFor any bug or issue with the mod feel free to comment down below.\n\n### Translations\n\nMod currently available in English and Italian Language.\n\nYou can use this mod in your **modpack** or **video**, just tell us.\nWe are open to any cool idea for **collaboration**.\n\n*Compatible **Minecraft versions**:\n**1.19.1**, **1.19.2**, **1.20**, **1.20.1**\nRequires **Fabric API**.*\n\n<br>\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/pixel-dream-studios-872788557553610802\">\n        <img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Plenty_of_Armors/BH_PoA_discord.webp\">\n</a>",
